Mail::DSPAM::Learning version 0.1
=================================

This is a module to annotate Web document in the ALVIS pipeline.

Contains this :

    dspam-learn (for learning missed spams)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Or if you don't have the "make" program:

   perl Build.PL
   Build
   Build test
   Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the other modules and libraries:

	Mail::MboxParser
	Mail::Builder
	Email::Send
	Mail::Box::Manager
	Term::ReadKey
	File::Basename
	File::Path
	Net::DNS
	Sys::HostIP
	Module::TestConfig
	Getopt::Long
	Pod::Usage

EXAMPLE

Go into the example directory and run dspam-learn-example (it don't
really send messages to your dspam server)

